    <h1>Estrella, Alexandra Jose B.</h1>
    <h2>BSIT-MAA--INF242</h2>

    <p>
        Hello! My name is Alexa. I am a 2nd year BSIT-MAA student who loves animation and drawing alike! I usually spend my free time playing games, drawing and watching animation from cartoons to anime to movies.
    </p>
    <p>
        I chose BSIT-MAA in NU because I wanted to go to a school who offers multimedia and a low tuition price. Many art focused schools are too expensive for father who's the only one supporting my studies as of the moment. However, the curriculum wasn't what I had expected But I'm still continue studying here to graduate on time and support my father for all the things he has done for me.
    </p>
